Package: ResearchTransparencyStatement
Title: Producing Research Transparency Statements for Journal Articles
Version: 0.0.0.9000
Authors@R: person('Marton', 'Kovacs', email = 'marton.balazs.kovacs@gmail.com', role = c('cre', 'aut'))
Description: A Shiny app that provides an easy-to-use interface for researchers who would like to produce their Research Transparency Statements for their journal articles. The package is developed to be complient with the transparency criteria of the journal Psychological Science.
